*Razliku* od drugih, on je jako zahvalan. (He is very thankful unlike others.)

Nismo mogli da otkrijemo *razliku* između dve stvari. (We couldn't discover the difference between two things.)

On je uočio *razliku* u boji. (He noticed the difference in color.)

Mnogi ljudi ne razumeju *razliku* između pojmova. (Many people don't understand the difference between concepts.)

On je uspeo da primeće *razliku* u tonu. (He managed to detect the difference in tone.)